BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p></p><p>The Wilmas are playing Mario Kart or Smash on the big screen! There will also be delicious cocktails (including non‑alcoholic ones). Feel free to bring your handheld so you can trade Pokémon\, visit other Animal Crossing islands\, or take care of your long‑forgotten Nintendogs during the waiting time between Mario Kart races or during breathers between dances! If you don’t have your own handheld console\, that’s of course no problem. The diversity has plenty of Nintendo Switch consoles to share.</p><p>The Wilmas are also looking forward to a pixel‑fun evening with you!<br/><br/></p>
